article.headline: Cohen, Tejada lift Lehigh past Army 75-70
article.linkText: Cohen, Tejada lift Lehigh past Army 75-70
article.story: BETHLEHEM, Pa. -- Jordan Cohen had 18 points as Lehigh edged past Army 75-70 in the quarterfinals of the Patriot League Conference Tourney on Thursday night. Lance Tejada added 16 points for the Mountain Hawks, while James Karnik chipped in 15. Karnik also had nine rebounds for the Mountain Hawks. Jeameril Wilson had 11 points for Lehigh (20-10). Tommy Funk had 22 points for the Black Knights (13-19). Matt Wilson added 17 points. John Emezie had 10 points. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap , using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
